==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: blacking
<hw>black"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Any preparation for
making things black; esp. one for giving a black luster to boots and
shoes, or to stoves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or process of making black.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blackish</ent>⟦br⟧
